Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.75,0:00:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai, let's walk home together.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.01,0:00:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we stop by the fire station?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.01,0:00:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously? That's no place\Nfor high school girls to hang out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.47,0:00:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I've got it, Mai. Let's go\Nto Daiku Coffee on the way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.40,0:00:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The system is pretty weird at that place,\Nso it might be a little confusing for you at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.78,0:00:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoink.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.69,0:00:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be there to show you the ropes though.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.09,0:00:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, Mai?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.05,0:00:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.43,0:00:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Asymmetry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.26,0:01:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's true, but it's a bit extreme!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.18,0:01:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about making a fashion statement!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.18,0:01:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.19,0:01:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She really threw me a curve this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.36,0:01:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai must be completely out of her mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.32,0:01:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what to say anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.08,0:01:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good God...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.71,0:01:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The heavens are on Mai's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.38,0:01:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Greatest friendship{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.46,0:01:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Super duper harmony{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.13,0:01:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}(na na na na na na na){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.76,0:01:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey! I'll say it{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.93,0:01:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You are my best best friend{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.89,0:01:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}(bright) Every time I poke fun and tease you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.23,0:01:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}(shine) You come and tease me back some more{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.69,0:01:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}(lan lan lan) There ain't\Nno better feeling in the world{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.44,0:01:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}(why) Even when bad things sometimes happen{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.82,0:01:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}(fine) I forget all of them around you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.07,0:02:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}(lan lan lan) We'll forever let the good times roll{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.58,0:02:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's not a problem being with you\Nevery hour of the day{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.04,0:02:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As if we're twins, child-parent,\Nor a pair of cloned cells{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.25,0:02:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Doesn't a friendship this good\Nmake love not so needed anymore?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.71,0:02:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait hold on this and that\Nare totally totally different things{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.59,0:02:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}(fight) Even after we've had a fight{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.05,0:02:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}(down) Or when I feel down in the dumps{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.34,0:02:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}(shock) All the times I wanted to be alone{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.80,0:02:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Before I know it there sitting beside me\Nmy wonderful friend till the end{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.85,0:02:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why is it, I wanna be at your side?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.60,0:02:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whenever we're together,\Ntime flies 100 times faster{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.69,0:02:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's so fun with you,\NI think it's almost too much fun{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.48,0:02:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's cuz you're such a good friend! Hey!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.40,0:02:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}(na na na na na na na){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.19,0:02:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's going on? Uh-oh we're synchronizing man!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.28,0:02:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's always a wild time,\Nwe make the people 'round us crazy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.07,0:02:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What time is it now? I think it's yodelayheehoo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.07,0:02:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's that even mean?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.33,0:02:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}SO-RE-DO-SHI-RA-{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.08,0:02:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Unbelievably, how to put it, awesome!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.54,0:02:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No matter what happens\Nwe are gonna be friends! Woohoo!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.04,0:02:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Greatest friendship{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.04,0:02:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Super duper harmony{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.71,0:02:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}cha chara chara cha cha-n{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.97,0:03:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"My Ordinary Life 68"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.39,0:03:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"My Ordinary Life 68"\NI wonder what I should put on today's menu...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.85,0:03:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what I should put on today's menu...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.85,0:03:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Green onions are cheap today,\Nso maybe something with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.07,0:03:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then again, Hakase kind of hates green onions...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.49,0:03:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nano! Nano!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.79,0:03:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nano!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.29,0:03:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Nano! I caught a crow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.88,0:03:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.13,0:03:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing!\NThat's dangerous! You'll get pecked!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.68,0:03:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.89,0:03:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.27,0:03:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not here...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.53,0:04:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I might die here...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.59,0:04:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not here, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.63,0:04:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did I lose my scarf?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.89,0:04:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Greetings. I'm Crow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.22,0:04:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.39,0:04:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah-choo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.73,0:04:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so impressed with how polite he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.48,0:04:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's 'cuz he's a crow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.36,0:04:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your words honor me greatly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.82,0:04:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think he drinks strawberry juice?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.90,0:04:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he would?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.99,0:04:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be so cute if he did!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.46,0:04:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.42,0:04:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's even killing insects for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.75,0:05:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing really. It's the least I could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.80,0:05:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a nice crow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.63,0:05:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What happened to your scarf, Sakamoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.39,0:05:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without a scarf, no one knows what he's saying!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.27,0:05:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll speak with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.40,0:05:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.11,0:05:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that he wants my scarf.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.95,0:05:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.70,0:05:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It ain't your scarf!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.25,0:05:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hakase... Did you actually put\NSakamoto's scarf on the crow?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.92,0:05:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, what a dilemma.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.68,0:05:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't you think that's\Na little cruel to Sakamoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.26,0:05:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, I'll make something!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.81,0:05:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.02,0:05:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.02,0:05:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Biscuit Number One!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.56,0:06:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's totally not a scarf!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.69,0:06:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, Hakase.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.27,0:06:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Biscuit Number One, what is he capable of?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.49,0:06:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good question, Crow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.57,0:06:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has a rocket punch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.53,0:06:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.95,0:06:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three, two!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.16,0:06:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blast off! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.21,0:06:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hakase, shouldn't you give\NSakamoto his s-scarf back soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.84,0:06:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.30,0:06:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We still have his left hand to fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.76,0:06:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three, two!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.93,0:06:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blast off! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.68,0:06:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Shinonome Lab"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.06,0:06:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Shinonome Lab" I'll kill 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.31,0:06:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Shinonome Lab"\NI'll kill 'em all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.40,0:06:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Shinonome Lab"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.32,0:06:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Shinonome Lab" My...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.32,0:06:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Shinonome Lab"\NWhat a fun day it has been.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.53,0:06:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My mischief has gone on for too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.99,0:06:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, give this scarf back to Sakamoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.87,0:07:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though it was short, I enjoyed\Nbeing able to speak with you humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.46,0:07:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crow...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.46,0:07:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't leave, Crow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.79,0:07:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hakase.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.38,0:07:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope someday, that we can meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.47,0:07:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until then, farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.10,0:07:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.39,0:07:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.19,0:07:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crow...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.52,0:07:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He took it with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.36,0:07:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}"Love-Like" {\an}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.91,0:07:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is impossible, Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.03,0:07:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it'll be fine. Just leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.41,0:07:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.54,0:07:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.79,0:07:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you trust me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.25,0:07:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not what I meant...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.92,0:07:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always completely trusted you, Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.92,0:07:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good. Then will you give me a hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.51,0:07:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.89,0:07:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Do you feel it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.43,0:08:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.44,0:08:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}"My Ordinary Life 69" {\an}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.42,0:11:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}"Yield" {\an}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.44,0:12:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Behind the Gym 1"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.78,0:12:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Behind the Gym 1"\NYesterday, I dug holes behind
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.99,0:12:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Behind the Gym 1"\Nthe gym and filled them with glue.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.36,0:12:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the gym and filled them with glue.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.32,0:12:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Powerful Glue"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.24,0:12:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Powerful Glue"\NI'll use this letter as bait and lure her into my trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.45,0:12:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Nano Shinonome"\NI'll use this letter as bait and lure her into my trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.29,0:12:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today is the day I capture Nano Shinonome.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.68,0:12:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.73,0:12:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.84,0:13:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea that Makoto Sakurai
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.05,0:13:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"My Ordinary Life 70"\NI had no idea that Makoto Sakurai
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.80,0:13:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"My Ordinary Life 70"\Nwas Ms. Sakurai's younger brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.97,0:13:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could use him to get\Ninformation about Ms. Sakurai.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.48,0:13:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.23,0:13:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can play Go+Soccer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.40,0:13:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.78,0:13:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sakurai.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.90,0:13:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.03,0:13:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't suppose you have a boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.57,0:13:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No future!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.12,0:13:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's always like this!\NI always screw up! I'm such a stupid man!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.54,0:13:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I don't, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.79,0:13:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't, but... I don't, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.17,0:14:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S... S...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.92,0:14:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sprouting!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.09,0:14:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not sprouting! Not sprouting!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.38,0:14:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.72,0:14:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, sorry. Forget I ever said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.51,0:14:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah! You know how to play Go+Soccer?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.39,0:14:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.77,0:14:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me guess, Mr. Takasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.19,0:14:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You like my sister, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.86,0:14:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-D-D-D-Don't be stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.70,0:14:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a former player,\NI'm just curious about you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.95,0:14:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Takasaki? You played Go+Soccer?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.08,0:14:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I did! You're looking at the MVP here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.75,0:14:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, our Go+Soccer club\Ndoesn't have an adviser yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.21,0:14:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you become our adviser,\NI'll help you all I can with my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.97,0:14:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, I never said... I liked her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.14,0:14:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you won't do it, I'll tell everyone\Nin the school that you like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.89,0:15:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.06,0:15:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about it? Will you be our adviser?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.94,0:15:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.27,0:15:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.65,0:15:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.95,0:15:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Advising is so annoy--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.03,0:15:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Everyone listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.28,0:15:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gonna move!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.45,0:15:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta chase him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.79,0:15:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Takasaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.95,0:15:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Behind the gym, Nakanojou fell into a hole!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.71,0:15:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.83,0:15:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need you to come right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.59,0:15:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hear about Mr. Takasaki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.50,0:15:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Takasaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.35,0:15:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad. Listen up...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.56,0:15:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.52,0:15:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakanojou didn't fall in a hole!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.85,0:15:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.98,0:15:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, he might be hole-in-one!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.69,0:15:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.65,0:15:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get this! All of his hair is missing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.07,0:15:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.94,0:15:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.40,0:15:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.11,0:15:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give it a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.86,0:15:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.61,0:15:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.36,0:15:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.28,0:15:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me what that's all about!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.99,0:15:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.66,0:15:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.24,0:16:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's more important to stop students\Nfrom spilling their teacher's private life!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.16,0:16:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a teacher, I can't... As a teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.13,0:16:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Takasaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.29,0:16:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.79,0:16:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't say anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.71,0:16:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be waiting for you to come and advise!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.22,0:16:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good one, dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.97,0:16:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Annaka, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.14,0:16:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.39,0:16:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time to hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.27,0:16:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.48,0:16:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...my duty as a teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.06,0:16:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.65,0:16:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.19,0:16:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I always thought it odd...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.69,0:16:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do feel bad for cutting his hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.91,0:16:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.78,0:16:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should probably help him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.12,0:16:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Behind the Gym 2"\NI should probably help him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.62,0:16:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Behind the Gym 2"\NHe still doesn't know that I was the one who did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.41,0:16:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He still doesn't know that I was the one who did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.04,0:16:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What's this?\N--Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.00,0:16:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What the heck? Where am I?\N--Huh? Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.25,0:16:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Where am I? This is weird!\N--Huh? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.34,0:16:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.30,0:16:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What the heck?\N--Huh? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.42,0:16:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I can't move.\N--Huh? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.17,0:16:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I can't move.\N--Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.05,0:16:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What the...?\N--My hair...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.93,0:16:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What the...?\N--Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.47,0:16:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What? What? What?\N--Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.64,0:16:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.26,0:16:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.68,0:16:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.10,0:17:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Swim, swim! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.06,0:17:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Shark, shark, bite! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.98,0:17:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Shark, shark, bite! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.11,0:17:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ That's when you go like this! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.82,0:17:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Life of Chitchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.49,0:17:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}"Daiku Bread" {\an}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.63,0:17:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Behind the Gym 3"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.63,0:17:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Behind the Gym 3"\NWhat the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.59,0:17:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.47,0:17:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.34,0:17:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.63,0:17:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.26,0:17:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Huh?\N--What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.26,0:17:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Huh?\N--Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.05,0:17:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What happened he--\N--Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.39,0:17:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What the...?\N--Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.51,0:17:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--My hair.\N--Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.22,0:17:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What, what?\N--Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.64,0:17:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What the...? This is weird!\N--Help me, please! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.60,0:17:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--That's so dangerous.\N--Help me, please! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.27,0:17:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--That's so dangerous.\N--What the...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.06,0:17:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.65,0:17:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--My hair.\N--Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.19,0:17:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.83,0:18:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"My Ordinary Life 71"\NToday's the day...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.50,0:18:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"My Ordinary Life 71"\NI won't make a jab at her jokes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.76,0:18:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Mai who's at fault in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.51,0:18:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's like a machine,\Nalways setting me up for the perfect jab!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.39,0:18:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, we'll be stuck in an infinite loop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.98,0:18:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're supposed to be girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.82,0:18:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, more innocent and pure than flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.03,0:18:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.07,0:18:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't even carry a normal girly conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.99,0:18:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting today, I won't make any more jabs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.79,0:18:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My resolve is more firm than a diamond.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.62,0:18:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah. Good morning, Yuuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.96,0:18:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Mai. Good mor--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.63,0:18:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Double glasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.67,0:19:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's intense! So intense today!\NWhy is she so intense today?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.18,0:19:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I will not lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.72,0:19:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We... We have to change!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.18,0:19:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai, {\i1}Selamat pagi{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.77,0:19:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good. Now's the time to break out the girly talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.19,0:19:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, Mai.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.57,0:19:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see yesterday's Muscle Theater?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.62,0:19:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh... Wh-Wh-Which is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.96,0:19:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Glasses... Glasses...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.00,0:19:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh gahhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.71,0:19:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's with these high-paced jokes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.09,0:19:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like she's expecting me to make a jab!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.51,0:19:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Don't do it, Yuuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.14,0:19:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.10,0:19:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What gives, Minakami?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.35,0:19:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got two glasses on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.52,0:19:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tanaka, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.10,0:19:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You stole it from me! That was\Nmy place to come in and make a jab!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.44,0:19:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! No, no! I'm not doing it anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.82,0:20:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not making any more jabs!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.03,0:20:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.49,0:20:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't today's first period language?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.91,0:20:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.20,0:20:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, did you hear\Nthat Ms. Nakamura fell over?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.70,0:20:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Is she okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.62,0:20:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.92,0:20:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't today's first period language?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.42,0:20:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just asked that a sec--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.92,0:20:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.38,0:20:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did she really just say the same thing twice?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.34,0:20:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So scary! This girl is incredibly scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.64,0:20:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Who's on day duty today?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.97,0:20:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.52,0:20:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.48,0:20:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take your sheet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.69,0:20:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get on with class today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.90,0:20:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Turn to page 82.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.23,0:20:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What's "take your sheet"?\N--Turn to page 82.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.44,0:20:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is "take your sheet"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.78,0:20:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's worse, everyone ignored it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.37,0:20:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, who wants to read this section?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.24,0:20:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.62,0:20:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Mai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.96,0:20:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, Minakami.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.12,0:20:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.46,0:21:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--A peaceful shade enveloped the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.76,0:21:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Sh-She's reading it, but...\N--A peaceful shade enveloped the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.84,0:21:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Sh-She's reading it, but...\N--A sprinkle of light glimmered
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.22,0:21:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Sh-She's reading it, but...\N--here and there around the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.59,0:21:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It was my first time there,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.47,0:21:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--She's reading it, but...\N--It was my first time there,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.56,0:21:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--She's reading it, but...\N--but somehow a feeling of nostalgia
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.35,0:21:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Reading, but... Reading, but...\N--but somehow a feeling of nostalgia
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.97,0:21:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Reading, but... Reading, but...\N--spread through my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.94,0:21:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She memorized it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.59,0:21:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.05,0:21:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jabs feel so...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.97,0:21:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...so...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.73,0:21:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...so darn good!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.49,0:22:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for raising my voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.21,0:22:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go stand in the hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.08,0:22:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.29,0:22:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.59,0:22:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is how it should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.05,0:22:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the path that I chose.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.13,0:22:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.89,0:22:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the path that Mai chose, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.35,0:22:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.73,0:22:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, all this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.86,0:22:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Contacts.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.03,0:22:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't even need glasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.96,0:23:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}"Kotatsu" {\an}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.63,0:23:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hakase. Hakase.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.39,0:23:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not here. Sleep in your bed or you'll catch a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.10,0:23:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hakase, you goof.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.44,0:23:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.98,0:23:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? A little longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.90,0:23:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She tricked me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.50,0:23:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In a desert with a red sinking sun{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.17,0:23:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is a big monster living peacefully{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.55,0:23:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It wakes one morning to a distant caravan{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.18,0:24:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hearing their bells, it suddenly yells{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.69,0:24:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to see the sea. I want to love people{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.32,0:24:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even monsters have hearts of their own.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.50,0:24:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's time to leave the desert behind{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.75,0:24:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For a place with love and sea{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.39,0:24:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A new sun will blaze again{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.56,0:24:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In a place with love and sea{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.50,0:25:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Word-Time"
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.67,0:25:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakamoto? You should get in bed, too, Sakamoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.46,0:25:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.22,0:25:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, she had to be carried.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.39,0:25:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm three of spades!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.89,0:25:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In President, I'm the worst card,\Nbut after a revolution I'm the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.65,0:25:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be a man and aim for President!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.23,0:25:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The next {\i1}My Ordinary Life {\i0}is Episode 18.{\an}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.57,0:25:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}"Narration: Kazuya Nakai"\NThe next {\i1}My Ordinary Life {\i0}is Episode 18.{\an}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.28,0:25:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}"Narration: Kazuya Nakai"\NLook forward to it!{\an}